<br>
Both my MAs use claw/fist, and one is prepared to dump claw (assuming I ever play again) soon as she sees damage drop off compared to fists. My nanomage MA briefly considered dual claws, but even at her lowish ATK rating, I can see the difference between even a grossly OE'd claw compared to her fists. <br>
<br>
